Megatron chuckled again. "Optimus Prime was new my dear Raptor. Where is
he now?" Megatron asked, spitting the challenge. He then looked around
him, noticing he was not in the most suitable position however. He had
accomplished their main objective however. He stopped swinging the mace,
and his shoulder cannon emitting a blast of stored energy straight at
the ground, pushing up the dirt, and creating a lot of smoke, encircling
Megatron. He then glew out of it, and towards Astroblast. "Astroblast,
transform" he ordered.
